{"tid":673212,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解電話騙案海報係用殘體字","createTime":"2018-05-21T15:42:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-30T22:57:40.000Z","uid":143151,"like":40,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"8e002a8707ab862a257ef6d4c6bc9bbaed3165da","tid":673212,"uid":143151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T15:42:33.000Z","msg":"我知通常俾人呃都係啲蝗<br />\n但咁係咪一個原因 將海報用殘體字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同一個概念 咁警訊係咪直接可以講普通話<br />\n<br />\n利申 非公屋 9成住戶係香港人<br />\n既然大部份讀者係香港人 <br />\n而且應該有好多呀婆呀伯都係受害者 點解要寫殘體字<br />\n過多十年可能全部Poster 寫哂殘體字<br />\n文化就係慢慢俾人一步一步侵略 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n應該要寫正體字 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n寫殘體字冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/21/234128_3514e6f6d0258ed2681fd9f1d5e4fe88.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F21%2F234128_3514e6f6d0258ed2681fd9f1d5e4fe88.png&h=b56df229&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"812a1050b33e91d68770dff784ccd708d7719061","tid":673212,"uid":56240,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T15:44:36.000Z","msg":"黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba537a25f7136ff367c54883102180794d9670b6","tid":673212,"uid":143151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"812a1050b33e91d68770dff784ccd708d7719061","tid":673212,"uid":56240,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T15:44:36.000Z","msg":"黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T15:47:39.000Z","msg":"佢個警務處 同委員會 仲要寫殘體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇到真係嚇親<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a83fea08955eef0ea5f6a7